\n  #sorelya-lipveil-{{ section.id }} .lipveil-subtitle {\n    max-width: 680px;\n    margin: 0 0 22px;\n    color: #333333;\n    font-size: 17px;\n    font-weight: 400;\n    line-height: 1.48;\n  }\n\n  #sorelya-lipveil-{{ section.id }} .lipveil-benefits {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    gap: 15px;\n    margin: 0;\n    padding: 0;\n    list-style: none;\n  }\n\n  #sorelya-lipveil-{{ section.id }} .lipveil-benefit {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: flex-start;\n    gap: 11px;\n    color: var(--lipveil-black);\n    font-size: 15.5px;\n    font-weight: 400;\n    line-height: 1.45;\n  }\n\n  #sorelya-lipveil-{{ section.id }} .lipveil-benefit-icon {\n    display: flex;\n    flex: 0 0 21px;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    width: 21px;\n    height: 21px;\n    margin-top: 1px;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    background: var(--lipveil-accent);\n  }\n\n  #sorelya-lipveil-{{ section.id }} .lipveil-benefit-icon svg {\n    width: 12px;\n    height: 12px;\n    fill: none;\n    stroke: #ffffff;\n  }\n\n  #sorelya-lipveil-{{ section.id }} .lipveil-benefit strong {\n    font-weight: 800;\n  }\n\n  #sorelya-lipveil-{{ section.id }} .lipveil-note {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: flex-start;\n    gap: 9px;\n    margin-top: 20px;\n    padding: 12px 14px;\n    border: 1px solid var(--lipveil-border);\n    border-radius: 12px;\n    background: var(--lipveil-soft);\n    color: #574c45;\n    font-size: 12.5px;\n    line-height: 1.45;\n  }\n\n  #sorelya-lipveil-{{ section.id }} .lipveil-note svg {\n    flex: 0 0 auto;\n    width: 17px;\n    height: 17px;\n    margin-top: 1px;\n    fill: none;\n    stroke: var(--lipveil-accent);\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width: 480px) {\n    #sorelya-lipveil-{{ section.id }} {\n      padding: 16px 2px;\n    }\n\n    #sorelya-lipveil-{{ section.id }} .lipveil-title {\n      font-size: 30px;\n    }\n\n    #sorelya-lipveil-{{ section.id }} .lipveil-subtitle {\n      margin-bottom: 20px;\n      font-size: 16px;\n    }\n\n    #sorelya-lipveil-{{ section.id }} .lipveil-benefit {\n      font-size: 15px;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n\n<div id=\"sorelya-lipveil-{{ section.id }}\">\n  <div class=\"lipveil-stars-row\">\n    <img\n      src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0891/4871/9429/files/stars-4.5-trust-pilot.svg?v=1747080316\"\n      alt=\"4.9 stars on Trustpilot\"\n      loading=\"lazy\"\n      width=\"96\"\n      height=\"16\"\n    >\n    <span class=\"lipveil-stars-label\">\n      Rated 4.9 Based on 4,200+ Reviews\n    </span>\n  </div>\n\n  <h1 class=\"lipveil-title\">\n    SORELYA™ LipVeil\n  </h1>\n\n  <div class=\"lipveil-badge\">\n    <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n      <path\n        d=\"M12 3l1.7 4.3L18 9l-4.3 1.7L12 15l-1.7-4.3L6 9l4.3-1.7L12 3zm6.5 11.5.9 2.1 2.1.9-2.1.9-.9 2.1-.9-2.1-2.1-.9 2.1-.9.9-2.1z\"\n        fill=\"currentColor\"\n      />\n    </svg>\n    The lipstick that finds your shade and stays out of your lip lines. \n  </div>\n\n  <p class=\"lipveil-subtitle\">\n    One sheer, buildable tint that works with your natural lip tone without the dryness, feathering or endless shade roulette.\n  </p>\n\n  <ul class=\"lipveil-benefits\">\n    <li class=\"lipveil-benefit\">\n      <span class=\"lipveil-benefit-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n          <path d=\"M5 12.5l4.2 4.2L19 7\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n        </svg>\n      </span>\n      <span>\n        <strong>All-day color that feels like a balm.</strong>\n        Comfortable moisture for lips that feel dry, tight or chapped never that heavy lipstick feeling.\n      </span>\n    </li>\n\n    <li class=\"lipveil-benefit\">\n      <span class=\"lipveil-benefit-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n          <path d=\"M5 12.5l4.2 4.2L19 7\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n        </svg>\n      </span>\n      <span>\n        <strong>Your lips aren’t the problem. Your old lipstick was.</strong>\n        Smooth, controlled color that stays on your lips instead of settling into the fine lines around them.\n      </span>\n    </li>\n\n    <li class=\"lipveil-benefit\">\n      <span class=\"lipveil-benefit-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n          <path d=\"M5 12.5l4.2 4.2L19 7\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n        </svg>\n      </span>\n      <span>\n        <strong>Stop buying nudes that pull orange.</strong>\n        LipVeil works with your natural lip tone, so the color looks flattering on you not just in the tube.\n      </span>\n    </li>\n\n    <li class=\"lipveil-benefit\">\n      <span class=\"lipveil-benefit-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n          <path d=\"M5 12.5l4.2 4.2L19 7\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n        </svg>\n      </span>\n      <span>\n        <strong>Your lips changed. Your lipstick should too.</strong>\n        A lightweight, forgiving finish created to flatter mature lips without emphasizing dryness or texture.\n      </span>\n    </li>\n\n    <li class=\"lipveil-benefit\">\n      <span class=\"lipveil-benefit-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n          <path d=\"M5 12.5l4.2 4.2L19 7\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n        </svg>\n      </span>\n      <span>\n        <strong>Apply once. Done for the day.</strong>\n        Fewer mirror checks, fewer touch-ups and no more wondering whether your color has moved.\n      </span>\n    </li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <div class=\"lipveil-note\">\n    <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n      <path d=\"M12 3a9 9 0 100 18 9 9 0 000-18z\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"/>\n      <path d=\"M12 10v6M12 7.2v.2\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n    </svg>\n    <span>\n      Start with one swipe for a soft, natural tint. Add another layer whenever you want a little more color.\n    </span>\n  </div>\n</div>"
