7 1.8 3 1.8\"/>\n          </svg>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"sorelya-benefit-card__content\">\n          <h3 class=\"sorelya-benefit-card__title\">\n            Comfortable Like a Balm\n          </h3>\n\n          <p class=\"sorelya-benefit-card__text\">\n            Lightweight color without the dry, tight feeling that makes\n            so many women give up on traditional lipstick.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n      </article>\n\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</section>",
